  triage:notes "Distinct from FTQ-001 (which covered workspace_root() in lint_sc_boundary_normalizes_* and lint_sc_runtime_normalizes_* tests, now closed). This is a new initial_pass finding for the project_workspace_root() use in the repo_root_discovery_walks_up_to_the_workspace_root test plus its live boundaries/ directory assertion at line 210. Only the integration/phase-A worktree was supplied; that single branch was swept. repeatable=false, so no full crate-scope sweep was performed beyond the cited file. Other project_workspace_root() uses in tests.rs (lines 421, 441, 497, 525, 568, 605, 626) drive hermetic fixtures via TempDir and are NOT in scope of this finding." ;
